  "original_title": "\u0d87\u0db8\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0d82\u0da0\u0db1 \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dcf\u0dc0 \u0d89\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Minister Kanchana apologizes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Power and Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekera has apologized for the fuel crisis. He was speaking at a media briefing in Colombo.",
        "The Minister said that although orders had been placed for fuel for the month of June, they could not be completed.",
        "Accordingly, there is a fuel crisis today, the Minister said. He also expressed his condolences to the President, the Prime Minister, the Cabinet and the government for giving him the responsibility."
      ],
